1122
01:24:42.251 --> 01:24:43.386
Come on. then.

1123
01:24:43.469 --> 01:24:45.515
We need to go
before he wakes up.

1124
01:24:55.002 --> 01:24:56.178
What's that?

1125
01:24:59.659 --> 01:25:00.704
I've been...

1126
01:25:01.748 --> 01:25:04.146
I've been waiting almost

1127
